data.description: Like NEW in Ballantrae Kirkwall! Open the front door and you will immediately fall in love with the openess and natural light this home offers! The beautiful great room has vaulted ceilings and opens to the MODERN kitchen complete with updated light fixtures, new hardware, stainless steel appliances, huge island, and tons of cabinet space! 3 bedrooms on the main level. The master suite sits privately in the back of the home! Huge walk-in master closet & tiled walk-in shower and separate vanities.  The back door opens up to a  flat, fenced-in backyard and covered porch perfect for entertaining, game days with family and friends and a patio for grilling. Upstairs is the 4th bedroom (or bonus space, home office, or workout room) with ample storage space including a walk-in attic. Ballantrae is a unique community with an award-winning golf course, lovely clubhouse, and the neighborhood pool is just a three minute car or golf cart ride!! Welcome home!
